          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "During a chase, Arkansas State Police spiked the tires and did a PIT maneuver on a Chrysler PT Cruiser on Halloween night, with a wild dashcam video as proof. Never in my life did I think I would ever write that sentence, yet here we are in 2022. Of all the cars I would pick to run from the authorities, a PT ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Cruiser",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/handpicked/1930s-cruiser-boasts-supercharged/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " would be toward the bottom of the list or not on it at all. But I’ve never accused criminals of having much sense, so there you go.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
